Programmed ingestion of turmeric has no adverse effects and reduces plasma level of hs-CRP, IL-6 and TNF- accompanying with increases albumin levels in hemodialysis patients.

 Turmeric can be considered as an effective anti-inflammatory supplement in hemodialysis patients.

